The third point is that the way CV is coded, you must re-cast it within 10 seconds (generally 9s as the 1s lingers too long to be reliable) or loose the ramped up effect. So if the adjusted recast was 7sec, you run the very easy risk of missing the next ramp up if you get resisted.<br />
